Depends: ${misc:Depends}, openmediavault (>= 1.0.0), fail2ban, whois
Description: OpenMediaVault Fail2ban plugin
 Protect OMV with Fail2ban. Fail2ban scans log files and bans IPs that 
 show the malicious signs -- too many password failures, seeking for 
 exploits, etc
